# Discovery & Personalization Engine Upgrade

Enhancing the VibeStream ecosystem with intelligent discovery tools and premium UI refinements for creators and viewers.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Shorts Detection**: I will implement automatic detection based on **aspect ratio (vertical)** and **duration (< 60s)**. This ensures that content uploaded via the standard flow is correctly categorized without manual input.
>
> **Tag Intelligence**: I will introduce a curated list of the **Top 50 Trending Tags** (e.g., #Gaming, #AIVibes, #Shorts, #TechReview). These will appear as autocomplete suggestions during upload to improve SEO and recommendation accuracy.
>
> **Channel Polish**: I will upgrade the Profile (Channel) UI to include "Bento-style" stats and more interactive banner elements.
>
> **Shorts Cinematic Parity**: I will refine the `/shorts` player to match YouTube's high-fidelity layout, including the right-side "tonal" action bar, integrated subscribe button, and high-quality ambient background.

## Proposed Changes

### Discovery Engine
#### [NEW] [lib/tags.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/lib/tags.ts)
- **Tag Library**: Define the canonical Top 50 tags for VibeStream.

#### [MODIFY] [UploadPage](file:///C:/GOLive/app/upload/page.tsx)
- **Shorts Logic**: Auto-set `is_short` flag in database based on metadata (`height > width` and `duration <= 60`).
- **Autocomplete UI**: Implement a suggestions dropdown for the tag input field.

### Creator Experience
#### [MODIFY] [SettingsPage](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/settings/page.tsx)
- **UI Refinement**: Apply glossy, high-fidelity styles to configuration cards.
- **New Meta**: Add fields for "Primary Channel Category" to help the recommendation engine.

#### [MODIFY] [Profile/Channel UI](file:///C:/GOLive/app/%5Busername%5D/page.tsx)
- **Visual Polish**: Refine the banner/avatar layout for a more "Expensive" aesthetic.
- **Shorts Grid**: Ensure shorts are displayed in a vertical 9:16 grid on the channel page.

### [NEW] Shorts Parity (Phase 20)
#### [MODIFY] [ShortsPage](file:///C:/GOLive/app/shorts/page.tsx)
- **Action Bar**: Redesign with tonal circular buttons and labels directly beneath.
- **Creator Overlay**: Integrate "Subscribe" button next to handle.
- **Cinematic Ambient**: Refine the background blur and dimming for better contrast.
- **Interaction Logic**: Implement Heart (Like) animation and share sheet.

### [NEW] Mobile Playback Excellence (Phase 21)
#### [MODIFY] [WatchClient](file:///C:/GOLive/app/watch/[id]/WatchClient.tsx)
- **Touch Targets**: Increase padding/margin for action buttons on mobile screens.
- **Ambient Optimization**: Ensure Halo Engine runs smoothly on mobile viewports.

#### [MODIFY] [Shorts Classification](file:///C:/GOLive/app/upload/page.tsx)
- **Logic Sync**: Fix the `is_short` auto-flagging to ensure vertical videos populate the shorts feed.

#### [MODIFY] [PWA Manifest](file:///C:/GOLive/public/manifest.json)
- **Asset Fix**: Supply missing 192x192 and 512x512 icons for better PWA support.

## Verification Plan

### Automated/Subagent Tests
- **Shorts Test**: Upload a vertical 30s video and verify it appears in the `/shorts` feed and the database `is_short` flag is TRUE.
- **Tag Test**: Type "Ga" in the upload tag field and verify "Gaming" appears as a suggestion.
- **Shorts UI Review**: Verify action bar and creator overlay match YouTube layout on mobile/desktop.
- **Mobile Watch Test**: Verify action buttons on the watch page are easily clickable on a 390px viewport.

### Manual Verification
- Verify that "Home" and "Trending" correctly separate Shorts from long-form content based on the new flags.
